title: The DIY Jacket Upgrade, Thank Me Later
description:
Unboxing The World's Smallest Phone
https://youtu.be/SSzyGCjH88o?list=PL7u4lWXQ3wfI_7PgX0C-VTiwLeu0S4v34

The Torch 2.0 coat heater is a DIY addition to any coat or jacket. It adds a battery pack and heating element to the interior of any jacket you choose. The install is simple and the Torch 2.0 is easy to remove. Since the install uses sticky velcro pads it's important to consider the material type of the coat you hope to install it in.

Torch 2.0 Coat Heater - http://amzn.to/2CBb3YH
